Heal Block

Type Category PP Power Accuracy Priority Description
15 - 18 — 100 0 For five turns, the user prevents the opposing team from recovering HP.

Effect

Block foe healing.

Affected Moves

The following moves are prevented by Heal Block.

Name Type Category PP Power Accuracy Description
Absorb 25 30 100 A nutrient-draining attack. The user's HP is restored by half the damage taken by the target.
Bitter Blade 10 90 100 A bitter slash that restores the user's HP by half the damage taken by the target
Bouncy Bubble 20 60 100 An attack that absorbs all of the damage inflicted.
Drain Punch 10 75 100 An energy-draining punch. The user's HP is restored by half the damage taken by the target.
Draining Kiss 10 50 100 The user steals the target's HP with a kiss, restoring its HP by over half of the damage dealt.

Jungle Healing 10 — — The user restores HP and cures any status conditions of itself and its ally Pokémon in battle.
